---

<BaseLayout
  title="Stem Cell Therapy in Miami, FL"
  description="Physician-supervised stem cell & regenerative therapy in Miami, FL. Brickell clinic treating arthritis, knee, joint & tendon pain plus exosomes."
  path={PAGE_PATH}
>
  <PageShell>
    <JsonLd schema={medicalClinicSchema} />
    <JsonLd
      schema={medicalWebPageSchema({
        name: "Stem Cell Therapy in Miami, FL — Strong Health Brickell Clinic",
        description:
          "Physician-supervised stem cell, PRP, and exosome regenerative therapy at Strong Health Miami's Brickell clinic for arthritis, knee, joint, tendon, and soft-tissue conditions.",
        url: PAGE_PATH,
        lastReviewed: PUBLISH_DATE,
        reviewedBy: DR_ANGEL_RIVERA,
      })}
    />
    <JsonLd
      schema={articleSchema({
        headline: "Stem Cell Therapy in Miami — Regenerative Medicine for Arthritis & Joint Pain",
        description:
          "How physician-supervised stem cell, PRP, and exosome therapy works at Strong Health Miami's Brickell clinic, and who is a candidate for regenerative care.",
        author: MAHADEV_MUKHERJEE,
        reviewer: DR_ANGEL_RIVERA,
        publishDate: PUBLISH_DATE,
        updatedDate: PUBLISH_DATE,
        url: PAGE_PATH,
      })}
    />
    <JsonLd schema={faqPageSchema(FAQS)} />
    <JsonLd schema={breadcrumbSchema(breadcrumbs)} />

    {/* Breadcrumbs */}
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="px-8 pt-4 pb-0">
      <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[12px] text-muted">
          {breadcrumbs.map((crumb, i) => {
            const isLast = i === breadcrumbs.length - 1;
            return (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                {i > 0 && <Icon name="chevron-right" size={12} class="text-text-subtle" />}
                {isLast ? (
                  <span class="text-gold font-semibold">{crumb.name}</span>
                ) : (
                  <a href={crumb.path} class="hover:text-gold transition-colors">
                    {crumb.name}
                  </a>
                )}
              </li>
            );
          })}
        </ol>
      </div>
    </nav>

    {/* Hero */}
    <section class="relative px-8 pt-12 pb-24 overflow-hidden border-b border-white/5">
      <div aria-hidden="true" class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#5DADE2]/15 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div aria-hidden="true" class="hidden md:block absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gold/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-5">
          <div class="flex gap-0.5">
            {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => <Icon name="star" size={16} class="fill-[#C9A84C] text-gold" />)}
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gold">4.9</span>
          <span class="text-[13px] text-muted">from 850+ Miami patient reviews</span>
        </div>

        <Tag>Miami Stem Cell &amp; Regenerative Medicine · Brickell Clinic</Tag>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-[52px] font-black text-cream leading-[1.08] mt-6 mb-5 max-w-[820px] tracking-[-1.5px]">
          Stem Cell Therapy in <span class="text-gold">Miami, FL.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-[18px] text-cream-muted leading-relaxed max-w-[680px] mb-3">
          Physician-supervised regenerative medicine at our Brickell clinic — stem cell–based
          injections, PRP, and exosome therapy for arthritis, knee, joint, tendon, and
          soft-tissue pain. Every plan starts with a real exam, not a sales pitch.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-[640px] mb-8">
          Miami is full of "stem cell" storefronts. We do it the way it should be done: a
          board-certified physician reviews your imaging, confirms whether you're actually a
          candidate, and sets honest expectations before anything is scheduled.
        </p>

        <Btn trackLead href={BOOKING_SMS_HREF}>Book Your Free Miami Assessment →</Btn>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted">
          In-person physician visit · On-site imaging &amp; labs · Bilingual (English/Spanish) · No memberships
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Byline (E-E-A-T) */}
    <section class="px-8 pt-2 pb-6 bg-surface">
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
        <AuthorByline
          author={MAHADEV_MUKHERJEE}
          reviewer={DR_ANGEL_RIVERA}
          publishDate={PUBLISH_DATE}
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Intro */}
    <section class="px-8 py-20 bg-surface-card border-b border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto">
        <FadeIn>
          <Tag>Real Medicine. Honest Expectations.</Tag>
          <h2 class="text-[34px] font-extrabold text-cream mt-4 mb-6 leading-[1.15]">
            Regenerative medicine in Miami, done as <span class="text-gold">actual medicine</span>
          </h2>
        </FadeIn>
        <FadeIn delay={100}>
          <div class="text-[16px] text-muted leading-[1.8] flex flex-col gap-4">
            <p>
              Search "stem cell Miami" and you'll find med spas, IV lounges, and pop-up clinics
              selling regenerative injections like a retail product — often with big promises and
              no physician in the room. Regenerative medicine done right is different. It starts
              with a diagnosis, not a package price.
            </p>
            <p>
              At Strong Health Miami, a board-certified physician evaluates whether stem cell–based
              therapy, platelet-rich plasma (PRP), or exosome therapy is a reasonable option for
              your specific joint or soft-tissue problem. We treat knee and hip arthritis, shoulder
              and rotator-cuff pain, chronic tendon and ligament injuries, heel and foot pain, and
              sports injuries — and we also offer exosome-based hair and skin rejuvenation.
            </p>
            <p>
              Just as important: we'll tell you when you're <em>not</em> a candidate. Advanced
              bone-on-bone arthritis, certain medical conditions, and unrealistic goals are all
              reasons we may recommend against treatment. That honesty is the whole point of seeing
              a physician instead of a sales desk.
            </p>
          </div>
        </FadeIn>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Conditions we treat */}
    <section class="px-8 py-20 bg-surface border-b border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto">
        <FadeIn class="text-center mb-10">
          <Tag>What We Treat in Miami</Tag>
          <h2 class="text-[34px] font-extrabold text-cream mt-4 mb-3">
            Conditions we evaluate for <span class="text-gold">regenerative care</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-muted max-w-[620px] mx-auto">
            The joint, tendon, and soft-tissue problems Miami patients most often ask us about.
            Every condition is assessed individually — candidacy depends on your exam and imaging.
          </p>
        </FadeIn>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {conditions.map((c, i) => (
            <FadeIn delay={i * 60}>
              <div class="bg-surface-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 h-full hover:border-gold/30 transition-colors">
                <div class="text-gold mb-4 p-3 rounded-xl bg-surface-raised border border-white/5 w-fit">
                  <Icon name={c.icon} size={26} />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-[15px] font-bold text-cream mb-2">{c.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-muted leading-relaxed">{c.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </FadeIn>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Therapies */}
    <section class="px-8 py-20 bg-surface-card border-b border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto">
        <FadeIn class="text-center mb-10">
          <Tag>Regenerative Options</Tag>
          <h2 class="text-[34px] font-extrabold text-cream mt-4 mb-3">
            The regenerative treatments we offer in <span class="text-gold">Miami</span>
